  <Method>
    <Step type="STEP" image="Ultimate%20Nachos_20260224_170815.jpg">Spread Tortilla chips on sheet pan, cover with shredded cheese and sliced black olives.</Step>
    <Step type="STEP" image="Ultimate%20Nachos_20260224_172337.jpg">Bake for 5-10 mins, until cheese is melted.</Step>
    <Step type="STEP" image="Ultimate%20Nachos_20260224_173310.jpg">Remove pan from oven, top with Taco Meat, Refried Beans and chopped avocado.</Step>
    <Step type="STEP" image="Ultimate%20Nachos_20260224_173506.jpg">Drizzle with queso and salsa. Top with green onions, cilantro and jalepeno slices.</Step>
